{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_08_01",
  "title": "fran",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ふ～ん、ふふ～ん……もう少し、時間もあるし\nあと一話分だけ、読んじゃおうかしら",
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1466.6666667000002,
          "startTime": 7.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2466.666666699999,
          "startTime": 8.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8633.333333300001,
          "startTime": 14.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、あの……すみません、読書中でしたか\n……あの。一体、何を読んでらっしゃるんですか？",
      "startTime": 15.672312228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "世界を股にかける、超一流スナイパーの漫画です\n凄く有名な作品ですよ、知らないんですか？",
      "startTime": 25.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、事務所でくつろぐのは構わないんですが\n一応仕事場なので、漫画は退社後にお願いしますね……",
      "startTime": 32.5679582914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "失礼ですね。これも仕事の一環です",
      "startTime": 37.4508383752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、私、誕生日企画で漫画描いたじゃないですか\nあれから仕事先で漫画のこと聞かれる機会が増えまして",
      "startTime": 45.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "なのでこうして、話題作や名作に目を通して\n日頃から情報収集している訳です",
      "startTime": 53.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言われれば、仕事と言えなくもないですね",
      "startTime": 56.7856678169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんも以前、漫画原作の映画に出てから\n漫画ファン向けの企画に呼ばれたりもしてますし",
      "startTime": 64.4963950793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "何が「ずっと漫画オタクだったんですよ～！」よ\nあの、話題作斜め読みのニワカが",
      "startTime": 73.2000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まあまあ……あとですね、事務所の本棚を\n漫画で埋めるのは、出来れば控えて下さい……",
      "startTime": 80.4058507601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "えー。うちの本棚、もう一杯一杯なんですよ\n少し置かせて下さい、他の子達も読んでいいですから",
      "startTime": 88.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "数冊ならいいんですけど、それ以上となると\n沙季や莉央さんあたりから、苦情がきそうなので",
      "startTime": 96.1927669842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "それはまたうるさそうな面々ですね……\n分かりました、ちょっと片付けます……",
      "startTime": 104.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9953528882
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（franさんの漫画好きアピールが功を奏した……）\n（かどうかは分からないが、やがて、とある仕事がきた）",
      "startTime": 114.0707257588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "私をご指名での仕事？　しかもアニメ絡みの？\nへえ……一体、どんな案件です？",
      "startTime": 124.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』という作品なんですが\nそれの2.5次元と言いますか、舞台版です",
      "startTime": 131.1224944432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "以前、トリエルの三人が主演して好評だったので\n第二弾もやるそうでして、それにぜひ出てほしいと",
      "startTime": 139.2891611099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "『ぷりエン』の舞台！？\n私がそれに出られるんですか！？",
      "startTime": 144.8333312989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ただfranさんにオファーがあったのは悪役でして\n資料によれば、敵の四天王の一人の『ネクロ』……",
      "startTime": 151.3766374589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "うそ、私がネクロ！？\nやります、絶対やります！！",
      "startTime": 157.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "悪役なのでどうかと思ってたんですけど\n答えは聞くまでもなさそうですね",
      "startTime": 163.5121615729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん。悪役が嫌われものってのは古い考えですよ\n最近はそっちにもファンが沢山付くんですから",
      "startTime": 171.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "私も『ぷりエン』子供の頃からずっと観てますけど\nシーズンごとに趣向が変わって、飽きないんですよね",
      "startTime": 177.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "子供向けの分かりやすい勧善懲悪をやりながら\n敵側のドラマもちゃんと描かれてて、深みがあって",
      "startTime": 186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "気に食わないところと言えば、お助け妖精キャラが\nどっかのガキに似てることくらいですかね",
      "startTime": 194.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……『ポンピピン』ってキャラでしたっけ\nkanaさんに似てるって、確か優も言ってました",
      "startTime": 200.9588566146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかしたら、kanaさんにもオファーがきてたのか）\n（そうなったら大惨事だったな……）",
      "startTime": 208.7000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、私が『ぷりエン』の舞台かあ……\n第一弾は普通に観に行きましたけど、良かったですよね",
      "startTime": 216.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、franさんも舞台観に来てたんですか？\n言ってくれたら、うちにきた関係者チケット渡したのに",
      "startTime": 224.3418725016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "お金を落とすところにはちゃんと落とすのがファンです\nそれに、関係者チケットもらって行ったら",
      "startTime": 232.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルにも感想言わないと気まずいじゃないですか\nそういうの気を遣いますし、なんか面倒くさくて",
      "startTime": 238.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "franさんらしいですね……でも稽古が始まったら\nどのみちトリエルとは顔を合わせることになりますよ",
      "startTime": 247.711765512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "そうでした……\n瑠依はたまによく分かんないし、優は底知れないし",
      "startTime": 254.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "すみれは良い子ですけど、ピュア過ぎてなんかこう……\n……ま、終わるまでどうにかやり過ごしますよ",
      "startTime": 265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "出来れば、この機会に仲良くなってくれると\n事務所のマネージャーとしては、嬉しいんですけどね",
      "startTime": 271.9976828895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
